author: Natasha Roy
title: Women who left N.Y. for China amid U.S. coronavirus outbreak document their journey
description: Tianran Qian and Feiran Lyu moved out of their New York City apartment to return to their hometown of Hangzhou, China, as the U.S. coronavirus outbreak worsened.
